1
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:26,990
[Love Endures]

2
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:29,610
[Episode 28]

3
00:02:31,910 --> 00:02:33,080
I will kill you!

4
00:02:46,430 --> 00:02:47,840
Give Yifei back to me!

5
00:02:48,430 --> 00:02:49,590
Give her back to me!

6
00:02:49,590 --> 00:02:51,470
You killed Yifei!

7
00:02:51,470 --> 00:02:52,750
It's all your fault!

8
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,400
(Dai Wei.)

9
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:20,470
(We received a report)

10
00:03:21,310 --> 00:03:22,470
testifying against you
for sexual assault,

11
00:03:22,470 --> 00:03:23,750
illegal detention,
and kidnapping for ransom.

12
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:24,870
Please cooperate with our investigation.

13
00:03:57,870 --> 00:03:58,520
Guan Chao.

14
00:03:58,630 --> 00:03:59,680
Your dad is here to pick you up.

15
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:00,400
You can leave now.

16
00:04:13,150 --> 00:04:14,150
You're not a kid anymore.

17
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,120
Won't you think about your future?

18
00:04:17,390 --> 00:04:18,510
I'm talking to you.

19
00:04:19,270 --> 00:04:20,160
Speak up!

20
00:04:24,870 --> 00:04:26,750
Yifei is dead.

21
00:04:26,750 --> 00:04:27,800
What do you want to do?

22
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:28,630
Do you want to kill Dai Wei?

23
00:04:28,630 --> 00:04:29,870
Are you sending yourself to death
as well?

24
00:04:33,070 --> 00:04:34,510
You disappoint me.

25
00:04:40,390 --> 00:04:41,830
I disappoint you?

26
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:44,240
She was a living person.

27
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,630
The one I loved.

28
00:04:46,830 --> 00:04:48,040
She is dead!

29
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:49,680
When she died,

30
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:51,630
I didn't even see her for the last time.

31
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,950
I couldn't do anything at all.

32
00:04:54,950 --> 00:04:56,830
I can only seek justice for her.

33
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,510
You don't even know what love is.

34
00:04:59,510 --> 00:05:00,600
You only love yourself.

35
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:02,240
There is no one else in your heart.

36
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:04,270
You are a selfish person!

37
00:05:23,270 --> 00:05:24,310
I'm leaving soon.

38
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,360
Take care of yourself.

39
00:05:59,190 --> 00:05:59,630
If you leave,

40
00:05:59,630 --> 00:06:01,240
what are you going to do
about university?

41
00:06:02,630 --> 00:06:03,510
If you leave everything behind,

42
00:06:03,510 --> 00:06:05,270
we will have to delay another year.

43
00:06:05,270 --> 00:06:07,360
How much time do we have to waste?

44
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:08,480
I don't care.

45
00:06:09,270 --> 00:06:10,870
You can't go!

46
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:13,310
Are you going to forsake your future

47
00:06:13,430 --> 00:06:15,600
for Huang Yingzi?

48
00:06:15,630 --> 00:06:17,240
If it were not for Huang Yingzi,

49
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:18,750
I may still not know

50
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:19,950
what I want to do in the future.

51
00:06:19,950 --> 00:06:21,510
I wouldn't even have come back with you.

52
00:06:21,510 --> 00:06:22,630
She's in trouble now.

53
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,120
I can't ignore her.

54
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:30,920
Yi.

55
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:33,310
Think about it again.

56
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:46,360
(Today is Monday, August 18th,)

57
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,800
(the eighteenth day
of the seventh lunar month.)

58
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,430
(The tenth day of the Beijing Olympics.)

59
00:06:49,430 --> 00:06:50,870
(The schedule is
already halfway through.)

60
00:06:50,870 --> 00:06:52,310
(The Men's 110m Hurdles)

61
00:06:52,310 --> 00:06:55,120
(will be held as scheduled
at Beijing Bird's Nest Stadium.)

62
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:58,160
(Chinese athlete Liu Xiang withdraws
from competition due to injury.)

63
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:16,720
(My daughter,)

64
00:07:17,310 --> 00:07:19,240
(your dad and I are out
to do some errands.)

65
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,950
(It's muggy and hot today.)

66
00:07:20,950 --> 00:07:22,630
(Just stay at home, don't go out.)

67
00:07:23,190 --> 00:07:25,390
(I will make crayfish
for dinner tonight.)

68
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:42,360
Yifei.

69
00:07:42,630 --> 00:07:43,360
Honestly,

70
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,390
I quite envy Yingzi.

71
00:07:48,830 --> 00:07:49,750
Because she can forget

72
00:07:49,750 --> 00:07:51,360
her unhappy memories.

73
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,510
But I can't.

74
00:07:58,270 --> 00:07:59,750
I still remember the first time
I saw you.

75
00:08:01,070 --> 00:08:02,310
You were dancing then.

76
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:05,750
You were wearing a little white dress.

77
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:08,750
You looked just like a little swan.

78
00:08:10,510 --> 00:08:11,800
I was thinking at that time.

79
00:08:12,510 --> 00:08:13,870
How could there be such a beautiful girl

80
00:08:13,870 --> 00:08:15,750
in this world?

81
00:08:21,390 --> 00:08:22,480
Thank you, Yifei.

82
00:08:25,950 --> 00:08:26,750
Yifei.

83
00:08:27,510 --> 00:08:29,160
Yifei, it was you who made me realize

84
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:32,360
that I could be the one who is loved.

85
00:08:37,150 --> 00:08:37,870
Yifei.

86
00:08:42,390 --> 00:08:43,320
I miss you.

87
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,320
Guan Chao.

88
00:09:03,790 --> 00:09:05,510
Keep your voice down, she's sleeping.

89
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:08,270
I woke up long ago.

90
00:09:09,150 --> 00:09:10,150
If I continue sleeping,

91
00:09:10,150 --> 00:09:11,750
wouldn't I become a sleepyhead?

92
00:09:14,750 --> 00:09:16,000
Where have you been?

93
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,120
Did someone die?

94
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,480
A colleague.

95
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:22,270
Who is it?

96
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:23,960
Someone from the factory.

97
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:24,840
You don't know them.

98
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,600
I grew up playing in the factory.

99
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:28,600
Is there anyone

100
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:29,720
that I don't know?

101
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:31,480
Well,

102
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,720
not a colleague.

103
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,960
It's the child of a colleague.

104
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,440
Child?

105
00:09:38,150 --> 00:09:40,200
Dying at such a young age.

106
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,390
What a pity.

107
00:09:42,870 --> 00:09:43,550
Yingzi,

108
00:09:43,910 --> 00:09:45,960
look, after the heat stroke,

109
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:46,720
you look haggard.

110
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:47,600
I will make some delicious food for you.

111
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:49,030
Replenish your nutrition.

112
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:50,550
No, thanks.

113
00:09:51,030 --> 00:09:53,200
I've been staying at home
these past few days.

114
00:09:53,789 --> 00:09:55,239
I want to go out for a walk.

115
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:56,150
No.

116
00:09:56,150 --> 00:09:57,480
It's too hot outside.

117
00:09:57,789 --> 00:09:58,959
I feel so bored staying at home.

118
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:06,200
I want to see Yifei.

119
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,150
I sent her a message

120
00:10:07,150 --> 00:10:08,750
but she didn't even reply.

121
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:09,510
Our university classes are starting

122
00:10:09,510 --> 00:10:12,150
in two weeks.

123
00:10:12,150 --> 00:10:13,910
If we don't get together now,

124
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,510
we might not have a chance later.

125
00:10:16,910 --> 00:10:17,790
I am going out.

126
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:27,390
Hurry up.

127
00:10:35,630 --> 00:10:36,510
Mingyu.

128
00:10:36,510 --> 00:10:37,630
I am Mr. Huang.

129
00:10:38,150 --> 00:10:38,840
Well,

130
00:10:39,270 --> 00:10:41,720
Yingzi is going to the wonton shop.

131
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:43,480
She said she was going to see Yifei.

132
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:45,720
You must be cautious.

133
00:11:05,550 --> 00:11:06,390
She's here.

134
00:11:14,790 --> 00:11:17,030
Why are you two manning the store today?

135
00:11:17,270 --> 00:11:19,120
Grandma's old illness has relapsed.

136
00:11:19,750 --> 00:11:20,270
It's back pain.

137
00:11:20,270 --> 00:11:21,320
She's resting at home.

138
00:11:21,870 --> 00:11:23,480
It's okay, we're both on holiday now.

139
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:24,390
We have nothing better to do.

140
00:11:24,390 --> 00:11:25,120
So we're helping out.

141
00:11:25,630 --> 00:11:26,200
Have a seat.

142
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,320
You haven't eaten, have you?

143
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,550
I'll make you a bowl.

144
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:29,550
Why did you come out

145
00:11:30,150 --> 00:11:32,440
without wearing your shoes properly?

146
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:40,200
I remember tying my shoes.

147
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:41,960
Oh, no.

148
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,720
My memory

149
00:11:45,030 --> 00:11:46,320
is getting worse recently.

150
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:47,790
I don't know what's going on.

151
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:50,390
Put in more seaweed for me.

152
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,910
Has Yifei contacted you guys recently?

153
00:11:53,910 --> 00:11:54,550
Yi...

154
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:56,720
Yifei is with the dance troupe.

155
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:58,390
They're performing in Jiangzhou.

156
00:11:58,670 --> 00:12:00,910
She could at least reply to my messages.

157
00:12:01,750 --> 00:12:03,240
I sent her messages on QQ

158
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,320
and text messages,

159
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:05,670
but she's not replying.

160
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:07,960
I'm a little worried about her.

161
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:09,150
What's there to worry about?

162
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:12,030
This is her first official performance.

163
00:12:12,030 --> 00:12:12,840
She must be busy.

164
00:12:14,270 --> 00:12:15,630
Have you heard about that girl?

165
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,080
How pitiful.

166
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:19,510
I heard she was only 18 years old.

167
00:12:19,510 --> 00:12:20,600
She's gone just like that.

168
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:22,720
We saw her last time.

169
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:23,720
She looked quite beautiful.

170
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:24,510
Eat up.

171
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:25,360
Here.

172
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:25,960
What a shame.

173
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:28,840
I heard she committed suicide.

174
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:30,240
She was so young,

175
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:31,960
I wonder what she was depressed about.

176
00:12:32,790 --> 00:12:33,510
Madam.

177
00:12:34,150 --> 00:12:35,720
Who did you just say committed suicide?

178
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:37,120
It's 12 yuan in total.

179
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,670
We haven't finished eating yet.

180
00:12:40,630 --> 00:12:41,670
She doesn't know.

181
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:43,150
Okay.

182
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:44,720
Quick, let's eat.

183
00:12:44,720 --> 00:12:46,030
I'll give you
two more bottles of drinks.

184
00:12:46,030 --> 00:12:46,910
I'm sorry.

185
00:12:48,630 --> 00:12:49,550
Thank you.

186
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:58,720
I haven't finished asking yet.

187
00:12:59,120 --> 00:13:00,750
Why did you chase them away?

188
00:13:01,910 --> 00:13:03,150
They have finished eating.

189
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:07,200
You obviously drove them away.

190
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:15,000
Zhuang Yuan.

191
00:13:17,150 --> 00:13:18,000
Mingyu.

192
00:13:20,030 --> 00:13:22,150
Why are you two acting so weird?

193
00:13:23,510 --> 00:13:25,390
Are you hiding something from me?

194
00:13:31,270 --> 00:13:32,080
Yingzi.

195
00:13:33,270 --> 00:13:34,360
Actually...

196
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:36,440
Huang Yingzi.

197
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:55,750
Look,

198
00:13:55,750 --> 00:13:57,320
you almost ruined the surprise.

199
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:02,870
When did you come back?

200
00:14:05,030 --> 00:14:05,790
Today.

201
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:23,200
Huang Yingzi!

202
00:14:32,550 --> 00:14:34,120
It's not easy for me to come back.

203
00:14:35,670 --> 00:14:37,200
Is this how you treat me?

204
00:14:38,840 --> 00:14:40,750
I'm afraid you'll still
be angry with me.

205
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:41,670
Yes.

206
00:14:41,670 --> 00:14:43,390
I am indeed still angry with you.

207
00:14:44,510 --> 00:14:46,630
I wanted to stay in the UK all my life

208
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:49,150
and never come back.

209
00:14:54,750 --> 00:14:56,480
Didn't you leave me a lot of messages?

210
00:14:58,750 --> 00:15:00,670
You should have a lot
to say to me, right?

211
00:15:05,870 --> 00:15:06,670
You don't want to talk?

212
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:10,150
I'm leaving, then.

213
00:15:23,120 --> 00:15:24,630
I saw you at the Internet cafe entrance

214
00:15:24,630 --> 00:15:25,840
that day.

215
00:15:26,790 --> 00:15:28,000
I did it on purpose.

216
00:15:28,870 --> 00:15:30,750
(I held hands with Zhuang Yuan
on purpose.)

217
00:15:31,600 --> 00:15:32,910
(I wanted to make you angry and leave,)

218
00:15:34,790 --> 00:15:36,840
(so I came up with such a stupid idea.)

219
00:15:38,270 --> 00:15:40,480
(I was worried you'd stop studying
in the future.)

220
00:15:43,390 --> 00:15:45,390
(I was worried you'd be
too depressed here.)

221
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:47,790
I was presumptuous

222
00:15:47,790 --> 00:15:50,200
and made you angry in this way
to chase you away.

223
00:15:53,910 --> 00:15:56,670
On the day you left,
I went down and chased after you.

224
00:15:57,270 --> 00:15:59,030
But you didn't see me.

225
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:02,840
Your car was going too fast.

226
00:16:03,790 --> 00:16:05,510
I kept calling out to you.

227
00:16:06,550 --> 00:16:08,200
Jiang Yi!

228
00:16:09,440 --> 00:16:11,440
Jiang Yi!

229
00:16:12,910 --> 00:16:16,150
Your car moved farther and farther away.

230
00:16:16,440 --> 00:16:18,320
In the end, I couldn't chase you.

231
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:20,840
The game you gave me,

232
00:16:21,440 --> 00:16:23,720
I played it over and over again
many times.

233
00:16:35,750 --> 00:16:36,870
(I saw it too,)

234
00:16:36,870 --> 00:16:37,960
(the Easter egg
you got me in the game.)

235
00:16:38,440 --> 00:16:40,670
I regretted it the moment I saw it.

236
00:16:41,510 --> 00:16:42,550
Can you forgive me?

237
00:16:42,720 --> 00:16:43,320
I shouldn't use

238
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:44,910
a presumptuous method

239
00:16:44,910 --> 00:16:45,960
to force you to leave.

240
00:16:45,960 --> 00:16:47,030
I was really too...

241
00:17:04,790 --> 00:17:06,480
I knew you were doing it

242
00:17:06,480 --> 00:17:07,640
to force me to go abroad.

243
00:17:10,790 --> 00:17:12,240
In fact, I regret it too.

244
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:17,160
I didn't get to see you one last time
before I left.

245
00:17:21,070 --> 00:17:22,440
Sorry.

246
00:17:23,240 --> 00:17:24,720
Sorry.

247
00:17:48,880 --> 00:17:50,400
During my time away,

248
00:17:51,960 --> 00:17:53,200
were you unhappy?

249
00:17:53,790 --> 00:17:56,240
You've only been gone for two months,

250
00:17:59,200 --> 00:18:01,750
but it feels like you've been gone
for an eternity.

251
00:18:03,510 --> 00:18:05,000
Moreover, I feel...

252
00:18:06,720 --> 00:18:09,200
I feel like many things have happened.

253
00:18:09,640 --> 00:18:10,790
Everyone is saying

254
00:18:12,070 --> 00:18:13,200
that Yifei

255
00:18:14,110 --> 00:18:16,440
went on a ballet tour.

256
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:19,270
But I couldn't contact her
no matter what.

257
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:22,880
Just like how I couldn't
get in touch with you.

258
00:18:23,720 --> 00:18:24,750
I feel...

259
00:18:25,400 --> 00:18:27,349
I feel like everyone seems
to be leaving me

260
00:18:27,349 --> 00:18:29,029
one by one.

261
00:18:34,160 --> 00:18:35,830
I'm back, am I not?

262
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:40,160
Well, since you're back here,

263
00:18:41,790 --> 00:18:43,110
will you still leave?

264
00:18:47,790 --> 00:18:48,590
No.

265
00:19:12,350 --> 00:19:13,110
Jiang,

266
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:14,920
that's how it is now.

267
00:19:16,070 --> 00:19:16,830
I've told you the specifics

268
00:19:16,830 --> 00:19:18,240
over the online chat.

269
00:19:18,550 --> 00:19:19,920
None of us know

270
00:19:19,920 --> 00:19:21,510
if she will remember it.

271
00:19:22,240 --> 00:19:23,590
We can only stay with her like this.

272
00:19:24,670 --> 00:19:26,350
We can't keep hiding this from Yingzi.

273
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:27,400
If she doesn't face it,

274
00:19:27,400 --> 00:19:28,510
she can never come out of it.

275
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:30,720
But what are we going to tell her?

276
00:19:30,720 --> 00:19:32,160
Who is going to tell her?

277
00:19:35,240 --> 00:19:36,240
Let me do it.

278
00:19:38,550 --> 00:19:40,240
If you really want to say it,

279
00:19:41,550 --> 00:19:43,030
you have to find the right time.

280
00:19:44,030 --> 00:19:45,510
That also depends on her condition.

281
00:19:54,680 --> 00:19:56,070
Why are you all here?

282
00:19:58,000 --> 00:19:58,960
Why did you come here?

283
00:20:00,270 --> 00:20:01,830
Here, it's your spare key.

284
00:20:02,160 --> 00:20:03,750
I thought now that you are back,

285
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:04,960
I should

286
