made the wrong choice once.

409
00:25:44,790 --> 00:25:45,720
This time,

410
00:25:45,960 --> 00:25:47,400
let's not make the wrong choice again.

411
00:25:49,070 --> 00:25:50,750
Let's not be separated again.

412
00:25:53,720 --> 00:25:55,750
Yes, I understand.

413
00:25:56,830 --> 00:25:58,640
I also want to go to Beijing with you.

414
00:25:59,720 --> 00:26:01,960
