416
00:26:03,750 --> 00:26:05,880
So before going there,

417
00:26:07,070 --> 00:26:08,590
I need to make it clear to you.

418
00:26:09,400 --> 00:26:12,030
What... What do you want to say?

419
00:26:15,270 --> 00:26:17,110
During the time I was away,

420
00:26:19,550 --> 00:26:21,920
