one of the two on the left.

437
00:27:25,030 --> 00:27:26,400
Neither is the one on the far right.

438
00:27:26,880 --> 00:27:28,070
She's probably the one in the middle.

439
00:27:28,550 --> 00:27:29,440
What do you think?

