543
00:34:24,030 --> 00:34:25,230
She missed me so much.

544
00:34:25,230 --> 00:34:26,000
(Yingzi.)

545
00:34:26,000 --> 00:34:27,320
She told me to dance well.

546
00:34:27,320 --> 00:34:29,630
(Take good care of Yifei for me.)

547
00:34:30,070 --> 00:34:32,070
