I've really gained a lot of weight.

588
00:36:23,000 --> 00:36:24,630
Of course, I need to manage
my physique.

589
00:36:24,630 --> 00:36:27,360
I will report to the university
with a pretty body.

590
00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:30,360
