that I want to do.

591
00:36:30,360 --> 00:36:32,630
I'm going to learn English.

592
00:36:32,630 --> 00:36:34,550
As soon as the university starts,
I will pass the CET-4.

593
00:36:36,150 --> 00:36:37,190
Boring.

