602
00:36:56,960 --> 00:36:58,000
that I created.

603
00:36:59,150 --> 00:37:00,070
Soon.

604
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:05,510
How about you?

605
00:37:07,110 --> 00:37:08,190
Me?

606
00:37:08,840 --> 00:37:10,630
I hope we can have

607
00:37:10,630 --> 00:37:11,670
a graduation trip.

608
00:37:12,110 --> 00:37:13,400
Go to the beach for a barbecue.

609
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:14,800
Watching the sunrise on the mountain.

610
00:37:14,800 --> 00:37:16,000
Eating and having fun together.

611
00:37:16,000 --> 00:37:17,190
Wait a second.

612
00:37:17,190 --> 00:37:17,760
That's not right.

613
00:37:18,230 --> 00:37:19,320
Let's say this beforehand,

614
00:37:19,320 --> 00:37:21,070
I won't be staying
in the same room as you.

615
00:37:22,480 --> 00:37:24,000
I... I think you've had
too much to drink.

616
00:37:24,000 --> 00:37:25,230
What... What nonsense
are you talking about?

617
00:37:25,230 --> 00:37:25,960
We... We ended up sharing a room then

618
00:37:25,960 --> 00:37:27,230
because I didn't have
my ID card with me.

619
00:37:27,230 --> 00:37:28,280
I was left with no choice.

620
00:37:28,280 --> 00:37:29,510
Let me tell you.

621
00:37:29,510 --> 00:37:30,550
When we were

622
00:37:30,550 --> 00:37:32,230
in Jiangzhou,

623
00:37:32,230 --> 00:37:33,230
we were staying in the same room.

624
00:37:33,230 --> 00:37:34,150
You...

625
00:37:34,150 --> 00:37:35,280
What's more,

626
00:37:35,280 --> 00:37:36,920
she snored the whole time.

627
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:38,320
I almost didn't sleep all night.

628
00:37:38,320 --> 00:37:39,480
Yingzi, you snore?

629
00:37:39,480 --> 00:37:40,480
