630
00:37:40,480 --> 00:37:41,670
You couldn't hear your own snore.

631
00:37:41,670 --> 00:37:42,480
You were snoring.

632
00:37:42,480 --> 00:37:43,280
Yingzi.

633
00:37:43,280 --> 00:37:44,230
Don't you snore?

634
00:37:44,230 --> 00:37:45,280
