and picking your feet.

635
00:37:45,280 --> 00:37:46,920
Who... Who would pick their feet
while sleeping?

636
00:37:46,920 --> 00:37:48,800
You two.

637
00:37:48,800 --> 00:37:50,840
Every time you two quarrel,
you will hurt someone else.

638
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:51,800
Yingzi.

639
00:37:51,800 --> 00:37:52,510
Stop throwing.

640
00:37:53,800 --> 00:37:55,320
Stop it.

641
00:39:58,840 --> 00:39:59,550
(Do not worry.)

642
00:40:03,230 --> 00:40:04,630
I will definitely cure you.

643
00:40:49,440 --> 00:40:51,070
Why are you here with me?

644
00:40:53,630 --> 00:40:54,760
What are you doing?

645
00:41:01,710 --> 00:41:02,920
Mr. Huang told us

646
00:41:02,920 --> 00:41:04,710
