647
00:41:04,710 --> 00:41:05,670
We were worried

648
00:41:05,670 --> 00:41:06,840
so we came to check on you.

649
00:41:07,800 --> 00:41:09,760
How long have I slept?

650
00:41:10,360 --> 00:41:12,230
Why am I so dizzy?

651
00:41:12,230 --> 00:41:14,400
I feel so sore all over my body.

652
00:41:14,880 --> 00:41:16,030
Well... Well, do you not

653
00:41:16,360 --> 00:41:17,440
