654
00:41:19,190 --> 00:41:20,440
What do I not remember?

655
00:41:20,800 --> 00:41:21,550
Yesterday,

656
00:41:22,800 --> 00:41:23,920
you guys...

657
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:26,070
Yesterday, we...

658
00:41:26,670 --> 00:41:27,960
What do you mean?

659
00:41:28,920 --> 00:41:30,760
After getting the admission notice,

660
00:41:30,760 --> 00:41:32,480
didn't the four of us
go out to have fun?

661
00:41:33,000 --> 00:41:34,320
Our destination was Jiangzhou.

662
00:41:34,320 --> 00:41:35,960
We went to see Yifei's performance.

663
00:41:38,880 --> 00:41:39,590
What's next?

664
00:41:40,710 --> 00:41:41,800
What's next?

665
00:41:41,800 --> 00:41:42,760
Are you silly?

666
00:41:42,760 --> 00:41:44,070
We took the train there.

667
00:41:44,360 --> 00:41:45,880
Then you took my potato chips.

668
00:41:46,400 --> 00:41:47,440
Then

669
00:41:47,440 --> 00:41:48,920
we were at the entrance of the theater.

670
00:41:48,920 --> 00:41:50,510
We looked at that poster.

671
00:41:50,510 --> 00:41:51,840
Zhuang Yuan and I made a bet.

672
00:41:52,150 --> 00:41:53,360
Zhuang Yuan lost in the end.

673
00:41:54,030 --> 00:41:54,710
I got it right.

674
00:41:55,000 --> 00:41:56,800
She was the most beautiful one
in the middle.

675
00:41:57,550 --> 00:41:59,550
Then we went in to watch
Yifei's performance.

676
00:42:00,920 --> 00:42:03,030
Yifei was so beautiful on stage.

677
00:42:03,670 --> 00:42:04,960
She danced extremely well.

678
00:42:06,400 --> 00:42:07,150
Guan Chao.

679
00:42:07,150 --> 00:42:08,960
Guan Chao, you even cried watching it.

680
00:42:10,590 --> 00:42:11,590
Later,

681
00:42:11,590 --> 00:42:12,880
I went to look for Yifei.

682
00:42:13,320 --> 00:42:14,840
We both chatted for a while.

683
00:42:14,840 --> 00:42:17,030
And we came back after that.

684
00:42:17,030 --> 00:42:18,150
I just went to bed then.

685
00:42:20,000 --> 00:42:20,880
Well,

686
00:42:22,400 --> 00:42:23,360
was it just the four of us?

687
00:42:24,030 --> 00:42:24,670
Of course.

688
00:42:25,110 --> 00:42:25,960
Who else was there

689
00:42:25,960 --> 00:42:26,760
