694
00:42:39,590 --> 00:42:40,800
You're acting weird.

695
00:42:42,360 --> 00:42:45,630
It's fine.

696
00:42:45,630 --> 00:42:46,510
Well,

697
00:42:46,510 --> 00:42:48,400
